{
  "texts": [
    "We utilized 16 80GB-A800 GPUs for one epoch pre-training and two epoch fine-tuning.",
    "DeepSpeed (Rasley et al., 2020) was employed for memory efficiency, and the AdamW optimizer was used with a 1e-4 learning rate and a 5% warmup cosine scheduler.",
    "Gradient clipping was set at 1.0.",
    "The LoRA parameters dimension, alpha, and dropout were set to 64, 16, and 0.1, with a batch size of 8.",
    "During the pretraining, we combined all training data in Section 3 and performed one epoch training."
  ]
}